Class SodirSurvey

java.lang.Object
no.geosoft.sodirio.SodirObject
no.geosoft.sodirio.survey.SodirSurvey
public final class SodirSurvey extends SodirObject
A survey as modeled by Sodir.

This class is thread-safe.

  • Method Details

    • getStatus

      public String getStatus()
      Return status of this survey.

      Sodir description:
      Example of legal values:

      • Høring
      • Planlagt
      • Pågående
      • Pause
      • Ferdig

      varchar(100), corresponds to Sodir property seaStatus.

      Returns:
      Status of this survey. Null if N/A or unknown.

    • getArea

      public String getArea()
      Return geographical area of this survey.

      Sodir description:
      Geographical area in the Norwegian Continental Shelf. Legal values are:

      • Nordsjøen
      • Norskehavet
      • Barentshavets - Sør
      • Barentshavet - Nord

      varchar(255), corresponds to Sodir property seaGeographicalArea.

      Returns:
      Geographical area of this survey. Null if N/A or unknown.

    • getMidPoint

      public String getMidPoint()
      Return midpoint of this survey.

      Sodir description:
      Midpoint of maximum og minimum North / South position and for the East/West posistion. The midpoint is given in degrees and decimal minutes and using Norwegian notation for East (Ø), i.e 73'' 29.8' N, 33'' 15.7' Ø

      varchar(100), corresponds to Sodir property seaMidPoint.

      Returns:
      Midpoint of this survey. Null if unknown.

    • getCategory

      public String getCategory()
      Return category of this survey.

      Sodir description:
      Indicates what method that is used in the survey. If seismic source is used, the category is set to "Seismisk undersøkelse", if electromagnetic source "Elektromagnetisk undersøkelse" is set. Otherwise "Andre undersøkelser" is set. See also "Main type" and "Sub type".

      varchar(100), corresponds to Sodir property seaCategory.

      Returns:
      Category of this survey.

    • getMainType

      public String getMainType()
      Return main type of the survey.

      Sodir description:
      Main type of the survey. Legal values are:

      • Ordinær seismisk undersøkelse
      • Havbunnseismisk undersøkelse
      • Elektromagnetisk undersøkelse
      • Borestedsundersøkelse / Site survey
      • Grunnundersøkelse / Soil survey
      See also description of category.

      varchar(100), corresponds to Sodir property seaSurveyTypeMain.

      Returns:
      Main type of this survey.

    • getSubType

      public String getSubType()
      Return sub type of this survey.

      Sodir description:
      Sub type of the survey. Legal values are:

      • 2D
      • 3D
      • 4D
      • Ikke seismikk
      All values are relevant for the different main types, except of "Ikke seismikk" that is only relevant for , "Borestedsundersøkelse / Site survey", "Grunnundersøkelse / Soil survey".

      varchar(100), corresponds to Sodir property seaSurveyTypePart.

      Returns:
      Sub type of this survey. Null if N/A.

      varchar(100), corresponds to Sodir property seaCompanyReported.

      Returns:
      Company responsible for the survey. Null if unknown or N/A.

    • getVessel

      public String getVessel()
      Return vessel(s) used in the survey.

      Sodir description:
      Vessels used in the survey (main vessel = "hovedfartøy" and escort vessels = "følgefartøy"). The boats shown here are entered in the message sent Sodir by the company doing the survey.

      varchar(1000), corresponds to Sodir property seaVesselAll.

      Returns:
      The vessel(s) used in this survey. Null if unknown or N/A.

    • isAvailable

      public Boolean isAvailable()
      Return if the survey is classified as market available.

      Sodir description:
      Indicator which tells if the survey is classified as market available (see Petroleum regulation § 85).

      varchar(20), corresponds to Sodir property seaMarketAvailable.

      Returns:
      True if the survey is market available, false otherwise. Null in unknown or N/A.
